(9, 'Math, Engineering, Technology & Science Week: March 6-12', 'United States', '3', '6', '2022', '2022-03-06', '3', '12', '2022', '2022-03-12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '8', '43', '13', '46', '52', NULL, 'Weekly', 'Changes', NULL, 'https://dese.mo.gov/content/math-engineering-technology-and-science-week', NULL, NULL, 'About National Math, Engineering, Technology & Science Week', NULL, 'Math, Engineering, Technology and Science (METS) Week aims to raise awareness about the great work that’s done in the METS (also referred to as STEM) fields.\n\nThe National Science Foundation (NSF) ceased sponsoring this event in 1999. However, states picked up the  event.  \n\nBecause of this, the dates of this week can vary city by city and state to state. We’re using Missouri’s dates to keep it on the calendar. Check with your local government agency or educational institution to see if a localized week is planned in your community.', 'Missouri Department of Education', '  205 Jefferson St.', ' ', 'Jefferson City', 'MO', 'US', '65101', '(573) 751.4212', 'communications@dese.mo.gov', 'General Information', 'https://dese.mo.gov/contact-us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Approved', '2021-01-17 16:50:22', '2021-01-17 16:50:22'),
