(24, 'RMS Titanic Sinks (1912): April 15', 'Worldwide', '4', '15', '2022', '2022-04-15', '4', '15', '2022', '2022-04-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', '48', '47', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sinking_of_the_RMS_Titanic', NULL, NULL, 'About the Anniversary of the RMS Titanic Sinking', NULL, 'Today is the 110th Anniversary of the sinking of the RMS Titanic. April 15 marks the anniversary of one of the most famous tragedies of the 20th century - the sinking of the ship RMS Titanic.  At the time in 1912, it was the largest and fastest cruise ship ever built. It was on its maiden voyage that it struck an iceberg. \n\nOf the 2,224 people on board, only 706 people would survive. ', 'Historical Anniversary. No Sponsor.  No Sponsor.', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Approved', '2021-01-17 16:50:22', '2021-01-17 16:50:22'),
