(318, 'Fashion Week, Copenhagen (DK): January 28-31', 'Denmark', '1', '28', '2020', '2020-01-28', '1', '31', '2020', '2020-01-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '39', '12', '16', '67', NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Changes', NULL, 'http://www.copenhagenfashionweek.com/about/future-dates', 'Copenhagen_Fashion_WkF.jpg', 'Copenhagen_Fashion_WkE.jpg', 'About Copenhagen Fashion Week in Denmark', NULL, 'Copenhagen hosts the Nordic Region\'s largest fashion event, Copenhagen Fashion Week. As industry movers and shakers get dressed and ready for a week of sartorial extravagance, the runways come alive with a diverse cast of fashion talents — Danish and international, new and established, classy and street. Meanwhile, the trade fairs, CIFF, CIFF KIDS, CIFF Raven and Revolver boast upwards of 1,100 exhibitors representing more than 2,500 international collections in all categories of style.\n\nScandinavian fashion is known for its unique take on design, which marries modern elegance to playful aesthetics and conceptions of dress. A contemporary approach to fashion both is expressed in fresh silhouettes, innovative fabrics and sharp color schemes, all in unsurpassed qualities. These are some of the reasons why a large number of international buyers, designers and press attend Copenhagen Fashion Week twice a year.\n\nOf course, the other main attraction to see is Copenhagen itself. It\'s a cozy yet metropolitan harbor city that offers a rich array of design venues, cultural events, shops, cafés, bars and nightlife.', 'Copenhagen Fashion Week', 'H.C. Andersens Boulevard 27', NULL, 'Copenhagen', NULL, 'DK', '1553', '(+45)(0)70.20.30.68', 'press@copenhagenfashionweek.com', 'Media Relations', 'http://www.copenhagenfashionweek.com/contact', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yes', 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-03-01 04:20:49', '2021-03-01 04:20:49'),
(319, 'Fashion Week, Men\'s, Paris (FR): January 14-19', 'France', '1', '14', '2020', '2020-01-14', '1', '19', '2020', '2020-01-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '39', '12', '28', '67', '16', NULL, 'Weekly', 'Changes', ' ', 'http://www.parisfashionweek.com/', NULL, NULL, 'About Paris Men\'s Fashion Week in France', NULL, 'As part of the larger umbrella under Paris Fashion Week and one of the \"Big Four\" world-renowned fashion weeks, Men\'s Fashion Week in Paris targets specifically the attire for men. \n\nThis event showcases and sets the fashion trends for years and decades to come. Every well-established fashion designer is present at the Paris Men\'s Fashion Week. From official suits and blazers to more casual dinner and outside attire, there is something for everyone who follows the Men\'s Fashion Week in Paris.', 'Fédération Française de la Couture', '100/102 Rue du Faubourg Saint-Honoré', 'Paris 8e', 'Paris', NULL, 'FR ', '75008', '(+33)(0)1 42.66.64.44', 'info@modeaparis.com', 'Jimmy Pihet, Communication Manager', 'http://www.modeaparis.com/2/extras-38/Contact,18', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yes', 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-03-01 04:20:50', '2021-03-01 04:20:50'),
