(357, 'Hot Chocolate Day, Ntl: January 31*', 'United States', '1', '31', '2020', '2020-01-31', '1', '31', '2020', '2020-01-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '19', '52', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'https://www.thrillist.com/news/nation/national-hot-chocolate-day-deals-2020', NULL, NULL, 'About National Hot Chocolate Day', NULL, 'What better way to warm up a cold winter day than with hot chocolate? National Hot Chocolate Day is embraced by many restaurants, confectioners and fast food restaurants throughout the nation. At many you\'ll find free hot chocolate with purchase of something. ', 'Unofficial Event. No Sponsor. See the Cocoa Research Centre for History', 'Cocoa Research Centre', 'The University of the West Indies', 'St. Augustine', ' ', 'TT', NULL, '(868) 662.2002', 'info@cocoacentre.com', 'Media Relations', 'https://sta.uwi.edu/cru/contact.asp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-03-01 04:20:50', '2021-03-01 04:20:50'),
(358, 'Hot Pastrami Sandwich Day: January 14', 'United States', '1', '14', '2020', '2020-01-14', '1', '14', '2020', '2020-01-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '19', '52', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'https://www.sandwichtribunal.com/2018/01/national-hot-pastrami-sandwich-day/', NULL, NULL, 'About Hot Pastrami Sandwich Day', NULL, 'Hot Pastrami Sandwich Day warms up mid-January every year. The name pastrami is Balkan, from the word ‘pastramă’, the origins of which can be trace back through Greek to Turkish. This type of wind-dried beef has been a traditional food in Anatolia for centuries, probably predating the Ottomans.\n\nAmerican pastrami is usually made from the navel end of the brisket. It\'s cured and coated with a mix of spices such as garlic, coriander, black pepper, paprika, cloves, allspice, and mustard seed. After that, it\'s smoked and steamed. The hot pastrami sandwich can be traced back to 1887. ', 'Unofficial Event. No Sponsor.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-03-01 04:20:50', '2021-03-01 04:20:50'),
