(446, 'Oropharyngeal Cancer Awareness Day (US/CA): January 30', 'United Kingdom', '1', '24', '2020', '2020-01-24', '1', '24', '2020', '2020-01-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '20', '7', '52', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Changes', 'Thurs of HPV week', 'https://www.headandneck.org/hpv-awareness-week/', NULL, NULL, 'About Oropharyngeal Cancer Awareness Day', ' ', 'HPV Awareness Week in 2019 and have set aside one day to focus on Oropharyngeal Cancer, or cancer of the oropharynx. Typical causes include smoking or contracting the human papilloma virus. Its most notable symptom is a lump in the neck accompanied by a sore throat.  \n\nThe goal of the initiative was to increase public and practitioner awareness of HPV, HPV-related diseases, and the importance of HPV vaccination.', 'Head & Neck Cancer Alliance', 'PO Box 21688', NULL, 'Charleston', 'SC', 'US', '29413', '(866) 792.4622', 'info@headandneck.org', 'General Information', 'https://www.headandneck.org/hpv-awareness-week', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/headandneckcanceralliance', 'https://twitter.com/hncalliance', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5vS5iFn7dzIeJRVTwk8Gng', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-03-01 04:20:50', '2021-03-01 04:20:50'),
