(460, 'Peculiar People Day: January 10', 'United States', '1', '10', '2020', '2020-01-10', '1', '10', '2020', '2020-01-10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '38', '44', '52', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WEFfqvh3PFQ&feature=relmfu', NULL, NULL, 'About Peculiar People Day', NULL, 'On Peculiar People Day we are encouraged to appreciate and honor differences, and seek out the peculiar souls whom surround us, even those we ignore, mock, or dismiss.  It is a day to celebrate what makes each of us unique. \n\nIt’s possible this day was created to honor an anniversary within the religious movement known as Peculiar People, Plumstead Peculiars or Banyardites.  This phrase derives from the book of Deuteronomy in the Old Testament.\n\nThe protestant sect was created by James Banyard in the mid-nineteenth Century and was known for its pacifism and rejection of modern medicine.  \n\nToday the church is found under the Union of Evangelical Churches.', 'Unofficial Event. No Sponsor. See The Union of Evangelical Churches for topical information.', 'The Union of Evangelical Churches ', '36 Eastwood Road, Rayleigh ', 'Essex', ' ', 'UK', 'SS6 7JQ ', '(+44)(0)12 68,74.22.93', ' http://www.uec-churches.net/contact/', 'Media Relations', 'http://www.uec-churches.net/contact/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-03-01 04:20:50', '2021-03-01 04:20:50'),
