(839, 'Idiotarod, (Multiple Dates/Cities): January 30*', 'United States', '1', '30', '2021', '2021-01-30', '1', '30', '2021', '2021-01-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '45', '14', '39', '44', '52', NULL, 'Daily', 'Changes', 'Last Sat Jan', 'http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/14th-annual-idiotarod-shopping-cart-race-gallery-1.3783948', '5001_IdiotarodF.jpg', '5001_IdiotarodE.jpg', 'About the Urban Idiotarod or Idiotarod', NULL, 'Urban Idiotarods - or Idiot-a-rod - have been going on since 1994 in San Francisco. These urban shopping cart races are named after the Iditarod - the 1,000 mile long dog-sledding race in Alaska.\n\nThe Idiotarods are a funny tradition, in which five \"idiots\" are harassed to a grocery shopping cart/trolley and run through the streets of a city.\n\nSabotage is permitted and encouraged and a main objective. People trip each other, throw items and topple obstacles. The event is quite amusing.\nThe first Idiotarod took place in San Francisco in 1994, but today you can take part in an Idiotarod in  Ann Arbor, Asheville, Austin, Boston, Chicago, Cincinnati, Dallas, Denver, Iowa City, New York City, Phoenix, Portland, Salt Lake City, Seattle, St. Louis, Toronto, Los Angeles, Vancouver and Washington, D.C., with new cities added every year.  \n\nThe actual date in each city my vary. Date posted is for the New York City event. ', 'Check with your local City', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', '<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/qf6ml9ah8jM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/ER4Oh55LG8M\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/OLkYFG5dPT4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yes', 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-08-16 