(963, 'Public Domain Day (1790): January 1', 'United States', '1', '1', '2021', '2021-01-01', '1', '1', '2021', '2021-01-01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', '25', '58', '12', '46', '52', 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'http://www.publicdomainday.org', NULL, NULL, 'About National Public Domain Day', NULL, 'Public Domain Day celebrates intellectual property such as copyrighted works by legendary authors and other creatives whom have passed on or donated their works to the creative commons. Public domain works are available to anyone who wants to use or read them, free of charge.  These classic works often become the building blocks for new art and creations, whilst inspiring the hearts and minds of each new generation. \n\nCopyrights are annual. January 1 each year is the day when new blocks of the world\'s knowledge, information and beauty become freely available as copyright protection expires on the works of those whom have passed on.\n\nThe Copyright Act was signed on May 31, 1790 by President George Washington.', 'The International Association On the Digital Public Domain', 'Communia\nc/o Wikimedia', '0', 'Brussels, Ixelles', ' ', ' BE', '01050', ' ', 'info@communia-association.org', 'General Information', 'http://www.communia-association.org/about', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-08-16 15:30:51', '2021-08-16 15:30:51'),
