(1056, 'Tin Can Day (1810): January 19', 'United States', '1', '19', '2021', '2021-01-19', '1', '19', '2021', '2021-01-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', '19', '46', '52', NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'http://inventors.about.com/od/cstartinventions/a/tin_can.htm', NULL, NULL, 'About Tin Can Day', NULL, 'Tin Can Day celebrates the invention of tin cans on this day in 1810 by British merchant Peter Durand. A major game-changer in food preservation, tin cans revolutionized the food industry. The first commercial canning factory opened in England in 1813, thanks to John Hall and Bryan Dorkin.', 'Historical Anniversary.  No Sponsor.', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-08-16 15:30:51', '2021-08-16 15:30:51'),
