(1061, 'Travel, Shop for Travel Day, Ntl.: January 12', 'United States', '1', '12', '2021', '2021-01-12', '1', '12', '2021', '2021-01-12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '48', '46', '52', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Changes', '2nd Tuesday January', 'https://www.skyscanner.com/tips-and-inspiration/deals/national-shop-for-travel-day-flight-deals', NULL, NULL, 'About National Shop for Travel Day', NULL, 'There is something about a new year that causes travel queries to spike in mid-January. Obviously, people are thinking about someplace other than enduring the winter doldrums. Capitalizing on this trend and mindset, National Shop for Travel Day encourages travelers and dreamers to research places to go and things to do on their next vacation. \n\nCreated inn 2018, this date seeks to promote, like a Black Friday or Green Monday, the best travel deals available, when people are most likely to be shopping them. Bon voyage!', 'Travel Tech Association', '3033 Wilson Blvd #700', NULL, 'Arlington', 'VA', 'US', '22201', '(703) 842.3754', 'sshur@traveltech.org', 'Steve Shur,\nPresident', 'https://www.traveltech.org/contact', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-08-16 15:30:51', '2021-08-16 15:30:51'),
