(1063, 'Trivia Day: January 4', 'United States', '1', '4', '2021', '2021-01-04', '1', '4', '2021', '2021-01-04', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '22', '13', '58', '52', NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Same', NULL, 'http://users.erols.com/jbirch/rlb/memoryville.htm', NULL, NULL, 'About Trivia Day', NULL, 'Trivia Day was created by Robert I Birch, of Pun Corps, a holiday inventing company that uses numerology. For instance, Trivia Day is January 4 each year the T and R of \'Trivia\' stand for the numbers 1 and 4.\n\nThe date was chosen due to numerology. It is a testament to the collectors of vast information who seem to always have something interesting to say.\n\nTrivia Day continues despite the passing of its creator in 2005. ', 'Created by Puns Corps. No Longer Sponsored. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-08-16 15:30:51', '2021-08-16 15:30:51'),
(1064, 'Tu B\'Shvat (J): January 27/28', 'Worldwide', '1', '27', '2021', '2021-01-27', '2', '28', '2021', '2021-02-28', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '24', '38', '15', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Daily', 'Changes', NULL, 'http://www.chabad.org/library/article_cdo/aid/149854/jewish/The-New-Year-of-Trees.htm', NULL, NULL, 'About the Jewish Day of Tu B\'Shvat', NULL, 'Tu B\'Shvat in Judaism is the \'New Year of Trees\'. \n\nThe tree-metaphor is fundamental in Judaism which sees trees as a metaphor for people, divided into three parts: roots, then trunk, branches and leaves, and finally, fruit as the third part. \n\nEach portion of the tree has a metaphoric meaning that corresponds to people\'s lives, struggles and goals.', 'Jewish Religious Holiday: See True Torah Jews Ask a Rabbi service ', 'True Torah Jews', '183 Wilson Street,\nPMB 162', 'Brooklyn', 'NY', 'US', '11211', '(888) 560.9634', 'info@truetorahjews.org', 'Ask a Rabbi Hotline', 'http://www.truetorahjews.org/contact', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'LEEP', NULL, 'Pending', '2021-08-16 15:30:51', '2021-08-16 15:30:51'),
